154.52,"line":48},{"w":"win","s":154.52,"e":154.52,"line":48},{"w":"then","s":154.52,"e":154.52,"line":48},{"w":"I","s":154.52,"e":154.52,"line":48},{"w":"win","s":154.52,"e":154.52,"line":48},{"w":"then","s":154.52,"e":154.52,"line":48},{"w":"I","s":154.52,"e":154.52,"line":48},{"w":"win","s":154.52,"e":154.54,"line":48},{"w":"again","s":154.54,"e":154.56,"line":48},{"w":"too","s":154.56,"e":154.74,"line":48}],"lines":[{"s":11.28,"e":14.5,"text":"I came in booked as the best, check the name on the chest"},{"s":14.5,"e":17.08,"text":"Cold hand, hot blood, I was built for the test"},{"s":17.28,"e":22.06,"text":"Mind wide open, got a crown in my head Pioneer gleam, I see ten steps ahead"},{"s":22.06,"e":24.6,"text":"I don't chase, I replace, then I sit where they sat"},{"s":24.6,"e":27.14,"text":"Every loss I ever ate, turn my spine to a track"},{"s":27.14,"e":29.66,"text":"I got teeth in the grin, got the wind in the stride"},{"s":29.66,"e":32.18,"text":"When the room gets dark, I bring fire inside"},{"s":32.18,"e":34.68,"text":"I don't fall for the noise, I don't slow for the doubt"},{"s":34.68,"e":37.54,"text":"If I step in the lane, then the lane gets crowded out"},{"s":37.54,"e":40.4,"text":"Every bar lands clean, every move got a plan"},{"s":40.4,"e":42.94,"text":"I was made for the peak, not the small pot stands"},{"s":42.96,"e":45.48,"text":"Look at me now, look at me now"},{"s":45.48,"e":47.98,"text":"I bend and I bounce, I rise, no count"},{"s":47.98,"e":50.12,"text":"If I back up, it's tactical"},{"s":50.12,"e":52.66,"text":"If I pause, it's practical"},{"s":52.66,"e":54.94,"text":"Rest in the room, rest in the room"},{"s":54.94,"e":57.66,"text":"I turn every loss into fuel for the bloom"},{"s":57.66,"e":59.96,"text":"Rest in the room, rest in the room"},{"s":59.96,"e":62.74,"text":"If I fall, I come back with a thunderous boom"},{"s":62.74,"e":64.96,"text":"Rest in the room, rest in the room"},{"s":65.12,"e":67.74,"text":"Never give up, that's the line, that's the rule"},{"s":67.74,"e":70.02,"text":"Rest in the room, rest in the room"},{"s":70.06,"e":72.64,"text":"I win, then I win, then I win again too"},{"s":72.78,"e":75.76,"text":"I got mud on my shoes from the long, hard climb"},{"s":75.76,"e":78.28,"text":"Now they point at the sky when I walk that line"},{"s":78.28,"e":80.82,"text":"Every scar on my skin got a story to tell"},{"s":80.82,"e":83.32,"text":"I was down in the pit, now I'm ringing that bell"},{"s":83.32,"e":85.86,"text":"I don't beg for a break, I break through the wall"},{"s":85.86,"e":88.4,"text":"Turn a choco to gold when I answer the call"},{"s":88.4,"e":90.9,"text":"If the play needs patience, I wait with a grin"},{"s":90.9,"e":92.8,"text":"If the play needs a strike, then I strike"},{"s":92.8,"e":95.8,"text":"And I win, I'm all in, all gas, no fear in the chest"},{"s":95.8,"e":98.36,"text":"When they call me the challenger, I answer as best"},{"s":98.36,"e":100.98,"text":"And if quitting looks useful, then I use it like chess"},{"s":100.98,"e":103.48,"text":"Step back, set the trap, then I finish the quest"},{"s":103.48,"e":106.06,"text":"I learn from the hit, I learn from the slip"},{"s":106.06,"e":108.56,"text":"Even a loss can be a blade on the hip"},{"s":108.56,"e":111.12,"text":"So I breathe and I lock and I move when it counts"},{"s":111.12,"e":113.94,"text":"What looks like a fall can be part of the bounce"},{"s":115.7,"e":118.02,"text":"Blast in the room, blast in the room"},{"s":118.02,"e":120.84,"text":"I turn every loss into fuel for the bloom"},{"s":120.84,"e":123.06,"text":"Blast in the room, blast in the room"},{"s":123.06,"e":125.9,"text":"If I fall, I come back with a thunderous boom"},{"s":125.9,"e":128.12,"text":"Blast in the room, blast in the room"},{"s":128.22,"e":130.94,"text":"Never give up, that's the line, that's the rule"},{"s":130.94,"e":133.16,"text":"Blast in the room, blast in the room"},{"s":133.36,"e":135.82,"text":"I win, then I win, then I win again too"},{"s":154.34,"e":154.52,"text":"Blast in the room, blast in the room"},{"s":154.52,"e":154.74,"text":"I win, then I win, then I win again too"}],"duration":154.75999450683594,"source":"whisper","generatedAt":"2026-05-22T02:28:15.262Z","model":"whisper-1"}